# FALSE (mul overflow-as-truth, D9 s3): a Q32.32 product whose magnitude >= 2^63 is not
# representable; mul must DIE, never wrap. Here 2^62 * 2^62 / 2^32 = 2^92 overflows, so the
# high-limb range proof fires (=? breach). mul is inlined (division-free multi-precision) so
# this fixture needs no vendored module. a wrong number that flows is worse than a death. signum != res.
